plain lowercase:
  symbol foo
  symbol bar
  symbol baz
uppercase (still symbol type, semantics differ later):
  symbol Foo
  symbol BAR
  symbol Baz
underscore allowed:
  symbol _x
  symbol x_
  symbol x_y
  symbol _
digits in tail:
  symbol x1
  symbol abc42
  symbol x_3
question / tilde in identifier (Symta convention):
  symbol is_int?
  symbol ~x
  symbol x~y
language keywords are tokenized as their own type:
  if if
  then then
  else else
  elif elif
  and and
  or or
